Another critical feature is a list of "What should I work on Next?". This would be a list of suggested issues for a developer to work on in the order that they should be done.

This should take into account schedule needs, including scheduling between other developers, dependencies (ie. don't suggest an item with an unmet dependency) and arbitrary due dates (which could be Fix_by milestones).